      <h1 class='title'>Tax Ready Reckoner and Tax Relief Document</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 November 2002 vol 395 c25WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_25ws' title='Col. 25WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 November 2002 vol 395 c25WS' name='column_25ws' href='#column_25ws' rel='bookmark'>25WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0395P2_20021127_CWS_15'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gordon-brown' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0395P2_20021127_CWS_15' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gordon Brown' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gordon-brown" title="Mr Gordon Brown">The Chancellor of the Exchequer (Mr. Gordon Brown)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The Government are today publishing a document containing the estimates of the effects of various illustrative tax changes on tax receipts in 2003&#x2013;04 and 2004&#x2013;05 (plus 2005&#x2013;06 for indirect taxes) and estimates of the costs of the main tax reliefs in 2001&#x2013;02. Copies are being placed in the Libraries of both Houses, and are available in the Vote Office.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
